We’ve updated our app! Creating your favorite meal is now easier than ever. From selecting a restaurant, to placing the order, the new ordering experience is seamless.
Minor updates to improve app performance and user experience.

This release includes a handful of updates, including:
• Special instructions field to add special requests for your order. Find it in the bag screen.
• Clarify delivery instructions to your driver with building and special instructions fields in checkout.
• Get alerts about your favorite foods and promotions with push notifications through the app.
This release includes minor updates and changes to improve your Panda Express app experience.

This update includes improvements to the delivery order experience. Please make sure you are on the latest version of the Panda Express app to ensure the best user experience when ordering your Panda favorites!
Minor app improvements, including updates to location search.
